        <ul class="text-sm space-y-2 text-white/70">
          <li>📞 Điện thoại: TBD</li>
          <li>💬 Zalo: TBD</li>
          <li>📍 Địa chỉ: TBD</li>
          <li>🕐 Check-in: 14:00 | Check-out: 12:00</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-primary-dark pt-6 text-center text-sm text-white/70">
      <p class="text-slate">&copy; 2025 Hải An Villa Hotel. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
